    <div class="dn-cov-cell"><strong>Dnipro (1M)</strong><span>1-2 days · 120+ branches · 250+ lockers</span></div>
    <div class="dn-cov-cell"><strong>Kryvyi Rih (640K)</strong><span>2-3 days · 60+ branches · 80+ lockers</span></div>
