    <div class="dn-int-cell"><strong>Custom REST API</strong><span>Full documentation, sandbox, webhook support.</span></div>
    <div class="dn-int-cell"><strong>CSV / SFTP batch</strong><span>For periodic bulk processing.</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="dn-cta-row">
    <a href="/en/services/" class="dn-cta-btn dn-cta-btn-secondary">Full services portfolio →</a>
  </div>
</div></section>

