<section class="dn-sec"><div class="ctr">
  <div class="dn-chip dn-chip-dark">USE CASES</div>
  <h2 class="dn-h2">International brand categories using Kyiv hub for Dnipro region</h2>
  <div class="dn-uc-grid">
    <div class="dn-uc-card">
      <h3>EU D2C brands shipping into Ukraine</h3>
      <p>European Shopify/WooCommerce stores shipping into Ukrainian market without local entity. Send inbound inventory to our Kyiv hub via standard freight. We pick, pack, and ship via Nova Poshta to any region including Dnipro. Customs paperwork handled at onboarding.</p>
    </div>
