      <h3>Industrial B2B distribution</h3>
      <p>Automotive parts, industrial equipment, electronics distributors targeting Dnipropetrovsk industrial customers. Multi-SKU orders, B2B documentation, integration with 1C/BAS Ukrainian accounting systems via REST API.</p>
    </div>
